constituent: journey, Nelson, column, going, line, candlestick, lord, drop, king, jewel, ball
heisigStory: Column . . . candlestick. This character has the special sense of journeying to someplace or other.
koohiiStory1: In Medieval Japan, going to see your lord was often a long journey.
koohiiStory2: The fellowship of the ring is on a long journey through the depths of Khaz Modan. Imagine they walk through the hall of pillars, with only light being from their own candlesticks that. Soon they will meet much more light than they would ever want to...

myStory: chữ vãng. đi, đã qua. bước ngắn của chủ, chúa đi qua.
words: 往復(おうふく): round trip, coming and going, return ticket
